'''ADL''', '''Astronomsko društvo Labod''' (Slovenian for '''Cygnus Astronomical Society''') is the most active [[Slovenia]]n astronomical society. It organises astronomy camps, lectures for youths and similar events.<ref>http://www.adl.si</ref> 

